## Business Model

**Pricing (Module-Specific):**
- Procurement: Banded by PO volume (300 POs = £400/mo, 600 = £700/mo, 3000 = £1400/mo) + £200/1000 pages for Invoice AI
- HR: £4/user/month + training courses charged individually
- Commercial: £100/user + ~£25/application for subcontractor payment submissions (pricing TBC)

**Target Market:**
- Primary: Main contractors (Commercial app forces subcontractor adoption → built-in CRM pipeline)
- Secondary: Subcontractors and any size company for point solutions (Procurement, Site Management, etc.)
- Sector: Entire built environment

**Customer Status:**
- ~5 beta testers externally
- Milestone Group acts as alpha tester (100 users)
- Testing pipeline: StoneRise internal (80% bugs) → Milestone alpha (15% bugs + feature feedback) → Beta testers (5% bugs + broader feedback)

